author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Speed Apparel Says Qtrly Profit & Total Comprehensive Income Attributable HK$7.4 Mln

organizations.name: brief-speed apparel says qtrly profit & total comprehensive income attributable

text:
Feb 7 (Reuters) - Speed Apparel Holding Ltd:
* QTRLY PROFIT AND TOTAL COMPREHENSIVE INCOME ATTRIBUTABLE HK$7.4 MILLION VERSUS HK$7.1 MILLION
* QTRLY REVENUE HK$113.9 MILLION VERSUS HK$150.7 MILLION A YEAR AGO Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
